steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Input the New Item name
Select Job Type on NewJobPage
Click 'OK' button
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Get Header
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
click 'Manage Jenkins' link from Main page
Click Configure System link on ManageJenkins Page
Enter an email into 'SMTP server' field for 'Extended Email Notifications' section
Enter a port number into 'SMTP port' field for 'Extended Email Notifications' section
Click 'Advanced' button under 'Extended Email Notifications' section
Click 'Add Credentials' button under 'Advanced' settings
Enter a user name into 'Add Credentials' pop-up window
Enter a password into 'Add Credentials' pop-up window
Click 'Add' button under Add Credentials
Select created credentials
Check 'Use SSL' checkbox
Click the 'Default Triggers' button
Check 'Always' checkbox under Default Triggers section
Check 'Success' checkbox under Default Triggers section
Enter an email into 'SMTP server' field for 'Email Notifications' section
Click 'Advanced' button under 'Email Notifications' section
Click 'Use SMTP Authentication' checkbox
Enter a user name and password for 'SMTP Authentication'
Check 'Use SSl' checkbox for 'Email Notifications' section
Enter a port number into 'SMTP Port' under 'Email Notifications' section
Click 'Save' button
